description: SPSK offers a unique investment vehicle that aligns with AAOIFI Sharia-compliant guidelines, providing an ethical and religiously appropriate choice for investors seeking to avoid interest-bearing instruments. The ETF is built on the foundation of Sukuk, which are asset-backed financial certificates. Unlike traditional bonds, Sukuk do not involve interest, making them a suitable option for investors adhering to Islamic finance principles. SPSK is designed to mirror the performance of the Dow Jones Sukuk Total Return Index.
name: SP Funds Dow Jones Global Sukuk ETF
